    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 4th rank, you learn a new way to use your Inspiring Display. While aboard your ship, when a creature that can see or hear you fails an ability check, attack roll, or saving throw, you can use use your reaction to aid that creature provided it did not already have or use an Inspiring Display die this turn. The creature can then roll the die and add it to the result.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus. You regain any expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
